  <span class="hero-tag">Evidence-Based Investigation · Updated July 2026</span>
  <h1>Is OLSP Academy an MLM? An Evidence-Based Investigation</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">Half the people say it is an MLM. Half say it is legit. Who is right? The answer depends on how you define MLM — and the question matters more than you might think.</p>

  <div class="metadata-box">
